apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: myfirstpod
spec:
  containers:
  - name: my-container
    image: nginx:latest
    ports:
    - containerPort: 80

## Steps to create pod ##
1 Install Kubectl eksctl
2 Create cluster
3 Create manifest file for pod
  vi pod.yml

4 Create pod using command

  kubectl apply -f pod.yml

5 To check created pod

  kubectl get pods